data.name: label4.Text
data.value:
Browser our Vietnam cycling tours to select the bike tour that most suit you. You can either find your tour by destination or length of stay. If you find out an itinerary that just fits your needs perfectly, that’s great! Please send us an inquiry.
If none of our sample cycling tours meet your expectation and you would like to plan your own trip. Just fill out the form to tell us the things you want to see and do, the places you want to stay, we will customize another tour to fit your needs. Kindly note that we do not require any credit card details when you complete the form.
Submitting a tour inquiry is not an act of reserving a tour, but rather a way of establishing communication with our travel consultant who will be helping with your tour. Tour booking will be confirmed with payment only when you are totally delighted with your personalized tour plan.

data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
Bicycel Rental is the great way to explore the beautiful landscapes of the country, and to experience the real life of local Vietnamese people at slow pace.
Our website is designed to give you an idea of the wealth of bicycle tour possibilities we offer. We have suggested some itineraries for each region, and these can be used as a basis for your trip or you may prefer to create your own itinerary.
The following steps simply show you how to book a bike tour with us.

data.name: label5.Text
data.value:
Based on your inquiry and requests, a bike tour specialist will design a plan for your tour including details of hotels, sightseeing, dining, etc, and offer you a price that is quoted based exactly on your group size, travel days and the services we include in the package.
If you find our price high or low, that is possible that the hotel category or the hotel room, the boat, the restaurants are not in the line you expect. Please tell your travel consultant about this. He/she will make another quote which may come closely to your needs and budget.

data.name: label7.Text
data.value: Once you have read through the itinerary and our service proposal, we will answer any further questions and refine the tour or related travel service until you are totally satisfied. Just feel free to express your wishes, and take good advantages of your personal travel consultant’s experience and advice.

data.name: label12.Text
data.value:
A deposit is required to confirm the booking. The balance needs to be paid in full before the trip departure or the use of our service. If we receive your booking less than 30 days prior to the tour start date, the payment needs to be made in full when you confirm the tour.
The payment methods we accept include: Cash, Bank Transfer, Credit Card, Western Union and PayPal. Kindly note bank transfer may take up to 7 days or even 14 days before the money activates our bank account. This depends on the banks where your account and our account are open.
Please double check with our travel consultant to see if all the proposed trip services are still available when you confirm the tour.

data.name: label14.Text
data.value:
The booking process begins when we receive your deposit, at which point we can start to confirm the trip, the accommodation and related services for your trip. So please let us know as soon as you make the wire in order that we can launch the booking reservations.
It may happen that some of those proposed services are no longer available after your confirmation. In that case we will book similar service of the same category and we will inform you before we launch the booking reservation.

data.name: label16.Text
data.value:
Our travel consultant will send you the final version of your tour itinerary (Service Agreement) after all the tour services are confirmed by our local suppliers such as airlines companies, hotels, cruises…
We encourage you reading the Service Agreement carefully to make sure that all the details are reserved according to your requirements. Starting from that date, there will be fees for any adjustment or cancellation.

data.name: label18.Text
data.value:
Upon your arrival in Vietnam, you will be greeted by Vietnam Cycling local team and transferred to your hotel in town (if airport pickup is included on the tour). You can pass by our office for paying the remainder (for cash payment only) or we can come to your hotel to collect the money (for cash payment only).
If you have any question or need further information please do not hesitate to contact us.
